5. Dynamic vs Static
e An environment that keeps constantly changing itself when the agent is
up with some action is said to be dynamic.
¢ Aroller coaster ride is dynamic as it is set in motion and the environment
keeps changing every instant.
e An idle environment with no change in its state is called a static
environment.
e An empty house is static as there's no change in the surroundings when
an agent enters.
